text: Mike Larnach (born 9 November 1952) is a Scottish footballer, who played for East Stirlingshire, Clydebank, Newcastle United, Motherwell, Ayr United and Stenhousemuir. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards Category:Scottish footballers Category:East Stirlingshire F.C. players Category:Clydebank F.C. players Category:Newcastle United F.C. players Category:Motherwell F.C. players Category:Ayr United F.C. players Category:Stenhousemuir F.C. players Category:Scottish Football League players Category:English Football League players Category:People from Caithness Category:Sportspeople from Highland (council area)
